Instead of creating a separate InvoiceSplits class, you would want to make a PXCacheExtension of InvoiceSplits.

    public sealed class InvoiceSplitsExtension : PXCacheExtension&lt;InvoiceSplits&gt;
    {

	    #region UnitCost
